<div class="com-share" data-id="12579" data-title="《从公知变成商业节目的运营者，梁文道谈了谈他在想些什么》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/12579/medium/12579.jpg?1437716803" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/12579.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
